description:
Bon Iver's Justin Vernon considers the past and the future on SABLE, fABLE
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

As the year draws to a close, we share this clip from Justin Vernon's interview with Jill Riley, recorded on June 6, 2025. The Bon Iver frontman provides introspective thoughts about his own trajectory and about the passage of time itself.  

Watch the full interview here: https://youtu.be/IJtIZgslmqU
